@ADHDdesigner Post treatment:
Meditate, walk my dog twice a day, eat proper meals, hydrate, brush my teeth, sleep consistently. 

I didn’t do this all in one go. It’s been several years of establishing habits.

@LisaBro20141156 Shakes, eating a big breakfast before meds if you can manage it. 

I found with practice it can become easier generally too. 

Easy to eat high calorie food can help.

